::Feline::

She slowly came around and noticed she was lying on the table.  She 
looked to see HotRod standing there next to her. "Ohh...ah...sorry 
about that.  I just wasn't expecting..a..story..like that one. 
Forgive me."  She sat up and put her hand to her head.  Her head was 
still spinning. "I just never would have guessed that I had...ah." 
She decided to choose her words carefully,"That I had fallen for such 
a bot would have ever thought me worth his time. Let alone all that 
we did."  she looked down and sighed. "I never knew that such a bot 
existed let alone look at me." her voice getting softer and softer as 
she spoke.  Her eyes looking down and slightly away from him.
